cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use CareerOS in your work, please cite it as below."
title: "CareerOS"
abstract: >-
  An agent-native, LaTeX-first CV and cover-letter builder fused with a
  job-application pipeline that learns from a user's own CV and cover letter to
  produce tailored, ATS-safe documents. Runs locally inside any AI coding agent
  (Claude Code, Cursor, Codex CLI, Gemini CLI, ...) with no server and no API key.
type: software
authors:
  - name: "VaibhavKKM"
version: "0.1.0"
date-released: "2026-06-08"
license: AGPL-3.0-or-later
repository-code: "https://github.com/Vaibhavkkm/CareerOS"
url: "https://www.vaibhavkkm.com"
keywords:
  - curriculum-vitae
  - cover-letter
  - resume
  - applicant-tracking-system
  - job-search
  - latex
  - ai-agent
  - claude-code
